column5: We take great pride in hosting and providing the best experience possible and a good sleep for every guest. We keep prices fair and we book up fairly quickly throughout the year. This custom built home is only used for AirBnB and every room has premium mattresses. Master Bedroom has a $3500 Simmons Beautyrest Black King set, 2nd room has a $3500 Simmons IQ King set, 3rd room has a $2500 Serta I-Comfort Queen set. House has WIFI and Directv, with a 65-inch TV in living room and master bedroom.
column8: Elite Family Custom Home 5 Miles from Texas A&M
